/*------------------------------------------------------------------------
    File        : Returns the Production Qty for a Given Job & Item
    Purpose     :  Use History records or FG-Act to calculate

    Syntax      : Run GetProductionQty (job, job-no2, item, output qty).

    Description :

    Author(s)   : BV
    Created     : 09/25/2014
    Notes       :
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------*/
